  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sector-wide policies and planning to support SDG4</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This activity supports AP Member States to strengthen relevant capacity to develop, reform and systematically implement their education sector policies and plans, aligned with SDG4-Education 2030, covering from ECCE to sec-edu. Anchoring on evidence-informed policy development, it intends to ensure a system-wide life-long learning approach to effectively operationalize SDG4. BGK will provide technical and advocacy support under four areas: 
(1)	Reviewing, developing and monitoring the implementation of ESP in light of SDG4, integrating ICT;
(2)	Strengthening national capacities in learning assessments; 
(3)	Generating evidence to inform policies on inclusive quality ECCE.
(4) 	Promoting and monitoring of rights-based approaches in education and learning.</narrative>
  </description>
